# moth — integrate and administer

Integrate moth authentication into a Flutter app (email/password, Google
and Apple sign-in) and administer a moth server from the terminal.
{{end}}
moth is a one-binary authentication server for mobile apps. One instance
hosts many independent projects (one per app), each with its own users,
ES256 signing keypair and configuration. Apps talk to it through the
`moth_auth` Flutter SDK the instance serves itself at `/pub`; operators
talk to it through the admin SPA at `/admin` or the `moth` CLI.

